### 2. Ensure `tsconfig.json` supports ES Modules
Rollup and modern bundlers expect strict ES module interop. Ensure your `tsconfig.json` has `moduleResolution` set to `bundler` or `node16`/`nodenext` and `module` set to `ESNext`.

**File:** `tsconfig.json`

